\end{figure}

\end{document}
```

This code will create a bar chart with the specified data and caption. The `pgfplots` package is used to generate the plot. The `\addplot` command is used to define the data points, and the `nodes near coords` option ensures that the values on top of each bar are displayed. The `symbolic x coords` option allows the x-axis labels to be strings instead of numerical values.

